/* PROCEDURE NAME:  ZERO_256                                               */
/* MEMBER NAME:     ZERO256                                                */
/* INPUT PARAMETERS:                                                       */
/*          CORE_ADDR         FIXED                                        */
/*          COUNT             BIT(16)                                      */
/* LOCAL DECLARATIONS:                                                     */
/*          MVCTEMP           FIXED                                        */
/*          MVC               LABEL                                        */
/* CALLED BY:                                                              */
